<para style="p">A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Yahweh, who may stay in your tabernacle?</para>

<para style="q1">Who may live on your holy hill?</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Whoever walks blamelessly, does what is right</para>

<para style="q1">and speaks truth from his heart.</para>
